      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Maintained to a rigorous standard, it exhibits consistent mechanical performance and a well-preserved aesthetic. It serves as an exemplary choice for those seeking a sophisticated balance of reliability and prestige. We invite you to experience the integrity of this refined automotive asset.",
      "price": 34500.0,
